text: Ærest of usmere on heasecan beorh.
Of þam beorge on cuðredes treow.
Of þam treowe on þa dic.
Þonne of sture ðæt eft on þa dic.
Andlang dic þæt on horsa broc, andlang broces on cenunga ford.
Of þan forda utan wið þone wudu ðæt to kyne fares stane.
Of þan stane on hoccan stige.
Of þære stige on mær wylle.
Of ðam wylle on ða dic, andlang dic on sture.
Of windofre on ðone stapul, of þam stapole on þone weg.
Of þam slæde on lyttan dune.
Andlang weges þæt eft on us mere.
